'''眼睛色彩'''是指[[眼睛|眼睛]][[虹膜|虹膜]]的色彩，由虹膜中黑色素数量、黑色素种类（[[真黑色素|真黑色素]]與[[假黑色素|假黑色素]]<ref name="Prota"/>），黑色素的分布所决定<ref name="Wielgus">Wielgus AR & Sarna T. Melanin in human irides of different color and age of donors. ''Pigment Cell Res.'' 2005 Dec;18(6):454-64. PMID 16280011.</ref><ref name="Prota">Prota G, Hu DN, Vincensi MR, McCormick SA, Napolitano A. Characterization of melanins in human irides and cultured uveal melanocytes from eyes of different colors. ''Exp Eye Res.'' 1998 Sep;67(3):293-9. PMID 9778410.</ref>，為一種[[多基因遺傳特徵|多基因遺傳特徵]]。人類與其他動物的眼睛色彩，擁有許多[[表型|表型]]變異<ref name="Morris">Athro Limited website. Morris PJ. [http://www.athro.com/evo/gen/eyecols.html Phenotypes and Genotypes for human eye colors.] {{Wayback|url=http://www.athro.com/evo/gen/eyecols.html |date=20101204171925 }}</ref>。許多鳥類擁有鮮明的眼睛色彩，這些顏色是決定於其他的色素，如[[蝶酸|蝶酸]]、[[嘌呤|嘌呤]]與[[類胡蘿蔔素|類胡蘿蔔素]]<ref name="Oliphant 1">Oliphant LW. Pteridines and purines as major pigments of the avian iris. ''Pigment Cell Res.'' 1987 1(2):129-31. PMID 3507666.</ref>。

虹膜的顏色受三種主要原因影響，分別是黑色素在虹膜色素上皮細胞中的含量、黑色素在虹膜基質的含量，以及虹膜基質的細胞密度<ref name="Wang">Proc. IEEE International Conference on Computer Vision. Huiqiong Wang, Stephen Lin, Xiaopei Liu, Sing Bing Kang.
[http://research.microsoft.com/~stevelin/iris.pdf Separating Reflections in Human Iris Images for Illumination Estimation.] {{Wayback|url=http://research.microsoft.com/~stevelin/iris.pdf |date=20080911080205 }}</ref>。不論是任何顏色的眼睛，在虹膜色素上皮細胞中都含有真黑色素<ref name="Prota"/><ref name="Wang"/>；而色彩的變異一般是決定於虹膜基質中的黑色素含量。虹膜基質中的細胞密度影響色素上皮細胞所能夠吸收的光線量<ref name="Wang"/>。

==色彩決定==
===基因遗传学===
眼睛的顏色是一種由超過一個基因所遺傳的特徵<ref name="Sturm">Sturm RA & Frudakis TN. Eye colour: portals into pigmentation genes and ancestry. ''Trends Genet.'' 2004 Aug;20(8):327-32. PMID 15262401</ref><ref name="Grant">Grant MD & Lauderdale DS. Cohort effects in a genetically determined trait: eye colour among US whites. ''Ann Hum Biol.'' 2002 Nov-Dec;29(6):657-66. PMID 12573082</ref>，對人類來說，目前已知3個基因座（Locus）上的基因與眼睛的色彩有關，分別是''EYCL1''、''EYCL2''與''EYCL3''<ref>Rebbeck TR, Kanetsky PA, Walker AH, Holmes R, Halpern AC, Schuchter LM, Elder DE, Guerry D. "P gene as an inherited biomarker of human eye color." ''Cancer Epidemiol Biomarkers Prev.'' 2002 Aug;11(8):782-4. PMID 12163334</ref><ref>[http://www.athro.com/evo/gen/inherit1.html "Eye colour is more complex than two genes."] {{Wayback|url=http://www.athro.com/evo/gen/inherit1.html |date=20110110085910 }} Athro, Limited. Retrieved September 1, 2006.</ref>。這些基因與人類眼睛顏色的表形有關（棕色、綠色與藍色）<ref name="Morris"/>。雖然過去曾經認為棕色眼睛為[[顯性基因|顯性基因]]，藍色眼睛為[[隱性基因|隱性基因]]。但是事實上兩位藍色眼睛的親代卻能夠生下棕色眼睛的子代，顯示眼睛色彩的決定並非遵循普通的孟德爾遺傳法則，只是這種情形相當少見（大約1億人之中才有1位）。必須全部四個基因同時決定相同的色彩，才能產生單純的顏色，反之則出現混合的顏色，如藍綠色<ref name="Sturm"/><ref>http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/entrez/dispomim.cgi?id=227240</ref>。眼睛的色彩通常在嬰兒出生後大約6個月趨於穩定<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://chemistry.about.com/cs/howthingswork/f/eyecolor.htm |title=存档副本 |access-date=2007-01-11 |archive-date=2011-01-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110105221830/http://chemistry.about.com/cs/howthingswork/f/eyecolor.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

2006年，''EYCL3''基因座被解碼<ref name=BBC>Paul Rincon, [http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/6195091.stm Genetics of eye colour unlocked] {{Wayback|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/sci/tech/6195091.stm |date=20200202082834 }}, ''BBC News'', 20 December, 2006.</ref>。經由針對3839位對象的研究，科學家發現所有眼睛色彩中，有74%能夠以[[OCA2|OCA2]]基因({{OMIM3|203200}})附近的多組[[單核苷酸多態性|單核苷酸多態性]]（SNP；single nucleotide polymorphism）解釋。事實上，''OCA2''這一組基因早已為遺傳學家所認識，因為他們發現當這組基因產生異變之後，會令帶有這基因的人出現[[白化|白化]]現象(albinism)。較近期的研究顯示：與藍眼及綠眼相關的不同SNP組合還與[[雀斑|雀斑]]、[[癦|癦]]與[[痣|痣]]、[[頭髮色彩|頭髮色彩]]及[[皮膚色彩|皮膚色彩]]相關連。The authors speculate that the SNPs may be in an ''OCA2'' [[regulatory_sequence|regulatory sequence]] and thus influence the expression of the gene product, which in turn effects pigmentation. <ref name=OCA2>Duffy DL, Montgomery GW, Chen W, Zhao ZZ, Le L, James MR, Hayward NK, Martin NG, and Sturm, RA [http://www.journals.uchicago.edu/AJHG/journal/issues/v80n2/44159/brief/44159.abstract.html "A Three–Single-Nucleotide Polymorphism Haplotype in Intron 1 of OCA2 Explains Most Human Eye-Colour Variation"] ''Am. J. Hum. Genet.'' 2002 80:000, 2007.</ref>

